title: Value of shipments of salt in Canada 2020
summary: The Value of shipments salt in Canada is fluctuating all the time in 2020 .
Overall , it drops for nearly a half in the first Month , and oscillated till July .
Then , it rises to a bit higher than the Value in January till November and December .
gold: Chart shows the value of shipment of salt in Canada in the Year 2020 . We have a chart depicting dollar value on a month over month scale . With a lot of volatility int he starting months then a slight plateau in the summer months , approaching the winter months we have a dip but then a rocket highs for the end of the year .
